title: 5th Annual PETCO Chihuahua Races, Anaheim - Aug. 1, 2009 - Presented By Petco
description:
Subscribe to our channel:
http://bit.ly/12dY9oO
 
These little guys sure are fast, but who has the fastest Chihuahua? PETCO is on a quest to search for America's fastest Chihuahua! Find out who takes home the prize at PETCO's 5th Annual Chihuahua Races in Anaheim 08/01/2009!
 
Something extraordinary happens when pets and people connect. A unique bond is formed that results in something powerful, not only between pets and people, but in a way that makes the world a better place. Our promise is to nurture that relationship completely--mind and body.
